{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<p>Below are a series of images I’ve taken next to the same location captured by one of our Earth observing satellites, mainly <a href=\"https://landsat.gsfc.nasa.gov/landsat-data-continuity-mission/\">Landsat-8</a> or <a href=\"https://sentinel.esa.int/web/sentinel/missions/sentinel-2\">Sentinel-2</a>. I make these for no other reason than to enjoy the difference in perspective they offer and play around with satellite imagery.</p>\n<p>In putting them together, I mainly follow the workflow laid out in this <a href=\"https://medium.com/@robsimmon/making-sense-of-satellite-data-an-open-source-workflow-accessing-data-8f7f3c30f151\">series of articles</a> written by <a href=\"https://twitter.com/rsimmon\">Rob Simmon</a>. It involves using <a href=\"https://www.gdal.org/\">GDAL</a>, a library for working with geospatial data, to process the raw satellite data, and <a href=\"https://www.gimp.org/\">GIMP</a>, and open-source image editing software, to further enhance the image. I then use Instagram to stick them next to an image I’ve taken.</p>\n<div class=\"imageBlock\">\n    <div>\n        <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 900px;\">\n    <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 100%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url(&apos;data:image/jpeg;base64,&apos;); background-size: cover; display: block;\"></span>\n    <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;box-shadow:inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\" alt=\"Venice, Italy\" title src=\"/static/6ca3253c0e24574ab35be59865c73128/87bff/earth-img-venice.jpg\" srcset=\"/static/6ca3253c0e24574ab35be59865c73128/44804/earth-img-venice.jpg 225w,\n/static/6ca3253c0e24574ab35be59865c73128/a0022/earth-img-venice.jpg 450w,\n/static/6ca3253c0e24574ab35be59865c73128/87bff/earth-img-venice.jpg 900w,\n/static/6ca3253c0e24574ab35be59865c73128/8b017/earth-img-venice.jpg 1350w,\n/static/6ca3253c0e24574ab35be59865c73128/8bbae/earth-img-venice.jpg 1800w,\n/static/6ca3253c0e24574ab35be59865c73128/2b759/earth-img-venice.jpg 2048w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 900px) 100vw, 900px\">\n  </span>\n            <p>\n                <span style=\"font-weight: 600\">Venice, Italy</span> eft: Landsat-8 564 false color image captured 4/19/2015; Right: me 08/2015 right after I got pooped on by a pigeon.\n            </p>\n    </div>\n    <div>\n        <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 900px;\">\n    <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 100%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url(&apos;data:image/jpeg;base64,&apos;); background-size: cover; display: block;\"></span>\n    <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;box-shadow:inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\" alt=\"Denali, AK\" title src=\"/static/5c07a7cb39e06f39b442671fae1ea3ee/87bff/earth-img-denali.jpg\" srcset=\"/static/5c07a7cb39e06f39b442671fae1ea3ee/44804/earth-img-denali.jpg 225w,\n/static/5c07a7cb39e06f39b442671fae1ea3ee/a0022/earth-img-denali.jpg 450w,\n/static/5c07a7cb39e06f39b442671fae1ea3ee/87bff/earth-img-denali.jpg 900w,\n/static/5c07a7cb39e06f39b442671fae1ea3ee/8b017/earth-img-denali.jpg 1350w,\n/static/5c07a7cb39e06f39b442671fae1ea3ee/8bbae/earth-img-denali.jpg 1800w,\n/static/5c07a7cb39e06f39b442671fae1ea3ee/2b759/earth-img-denali.jpg 2048w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 900px) 100vw, 900px\">\n  </span>\n            <p>\n                <span style=\"font-weight: 600\">Denali, AK</span> A typically cloud-covered Denali from up there and down here. Top: a very luck me on 07/23/2017 Bottom: a similarly lucky Landsat-8 on 07/22/2017.\n            </p>\n        </div>\n    <div>\n        <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 900px;\">\n    <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 106.81167716084717%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url(&apos;data:image/png;base64,&apos;); background-size: cover; display: block;\"></span>\n    <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;box-shadow:inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\" alt=\"Figure 3\" title src=\"/static/b5b66210d245505bb29c4716a029e0bf/48396/figure_3.png\" srcset=\"/static/b5b66210d245505bb29c4716a029e0bf/39d7a/figure_3.png 225w,\n/static/b5b66210d245505bb29c4716a029e0bf/d45f3/figure_3.png 450w,\n/static/b5b66210d245505bb29c4716a029e0bf/48396/figure_3.png 900w,\n/static/b5b66210d245505bb29c4716a029e0bf/14262/figure_3.png 1350w,\n/static/b5b66210d245505bb29c4716a029e0bf/81964/figure_3.png 1747w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 900px) 100vw, 900px\">\n  </span>\n            <p>\n                <span style=\"font-weight: 600\">Figure 3:</span> Map of\n                small-scale mining (SSM) activity derived from the classification of\n                the Landsat-7 and -8 2013 and 2015 imagery in the context of\n                large-scale concessions, large-scale mines, unofficial small-scale\n                mining concessions, and unsuitable small-scale mining areas.\n            </p>\n    </div>\n    <div>\n        <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 900px;\">\n    <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 106.81167716084717%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url(&apos;data:image/png;base64,&apos;); background-size: cover; display: block;\"></span>\n    <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;box-shadow:inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\" alt=\"Figure 4\" title src=\"/static/309f55cddd28a3dcfb7916de883d2888/48396/figure_4.png\" srcset=\"/static/309f55cddd28a3dcfb7916de883d2888/39d7a/figure_4.png 225w,\n/static/309f55cddd28a3dcfb7916de883d2888/d45f3/figure_4.png 450w,\n/static/309f55cddd28a3dcfb7916de883d2888/48396/figure_4.png 900w,\n/static/309f55cddd28a3dcfb7916de883d2888/14262/figure_4.png 1350w,\n/static/309f55cddd28a3dcfb7916de883d2888/81964/figure_4.png 1747w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 900px) 100vw, 900px\">\n  </span>\n            <p>\n                <span style=\"font-weight: 600\">Figure 4:</span> Northwest region\n                of the study area shown with the small-scale mining (SSM) derived from the 2013 and 2015 Landsat-7 and &#x2013;-8 imagery in the context of the surrounding cities, large-scale mines, large-scale mining concessions, unofficial small-scale mining concessions, and unsuitable small-scale mining areas.\n            </p>\n    </div>\n    <div>\n        <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 900px;\">\n    <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 106.81167716084717%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url(&apos;data:image/png;base64,&apos;); background-size: cover; display: block;\"></span>\n    <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;box-shadow:inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\" alt=\"Figure 5\" title src=\"/static/cdebfff7cdf8c205593f92d527ff3a69/48396/figure_5.png\" srcset=\"/static/cdebfff7cdf8c205593f92d527ff3a69/39d7a/figure_5.png 225w,\n/static/cdebfff7cdf8c205593f92d527ff3a69/d45f3/figure_5.png 450w,\n/static/cdebfff7cdf8c205593f92d527ff3a69/48396/figure_5.png 900w,\n/static/cdebfff7cdf8c205593f92d527ff3a69/14262/figure_5.png 1350w,\n/static/cdebfff7cdf8c205593f92d527ff3a69/81964/figure_5.png 1747w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 900px) 100vw, 900px\">\n  </span>\n            <p>\n                <span style=\"font-weight: 600\">Figure 5:</span> Southwest region\n                of the study area shown with the small-scale mining (SSM) derived from the 2013 and 2015 Landsat-7 and -8 imagery in the context of the\n                surrounding cities, large-scale mines, large-scale mining concessions, unofficial small-scale mining concessions, and unsuitable small-scale mining areas.\n            </p>\n    </div>\n    <div>\n        <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 900px;\">\n    <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 106.81167716084717%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url(&apos;data:image/png;base64,&apos;); background-size: cover; display: block;\"></span>\n    <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;box-shadow:inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\" alt=\"Figure 6\" title src=\"/static/cc6051c45f961675c51cbceedce71e50/48396/figure_6.png\" srcset=\"/static/cc6051c45f961675c51cbceedce71e50/39d7a/figure_6.png 225w,\n/static/cc6051c45f961675c51cbceedce71e50/d45f3/figure_6.png 450w,\n/static/cc6051c45f961675c51cbceedce71e50/48396/figure_6.png 900w,\n/static/cc6051c45f961675c51cbceedce71e50/14262/figure_6.png 1350w,\n/static/cc6051c45f961675c51cbceedce71e50/81964/figure_6.png 1747w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 900px) 100vw, 900px\">\n  </span>\n            <p>\n                <span style=\"font-weight: 600\">Figure 6:</span> Northeast region\n                of the study area shown with the small-scale mining (SSM) derived from the 2013 and 2015 Landsat-7 and -8 imagery in the context of the\n                surrounding cities, large-scale mines, large-scale mining concessions, unofficial small-scale mining concessions, and unsuitable small-scale mining areas.\n            </p>\n    </div>\n</div>","frontmatter":{"title":"Earth Images","myRole":""}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/projects/earth-images/"}}